USE pnpm lint && pnpm lint:fix BEFORE EVERY COMMIT!!!

Run both from **repository root**. Order: run `pnpm lint` (check), then `pnpm lint:fix` (auto-fix).

Note: root `pnpm lint:fix` runs:
- `@meriter/api`: script `lint` (already includes `--fix` in api's eslint command)
- `@meriter/web`: script `lint:fix`

